<whtranslation key="~whDemoShortDesccoderage">
View Code Rage Conference schedule with times translated 
for your location, i.e. time zone adjustments done for you.
</whtranslation>

<whtranslation key="~whDemoLongDescCodeRage">
During the Embarcadero Live Code Rage Conference, 
this demo provides schedule details with times adjusted for your time zone. 
During the rest of the year, this demo provides a search engine 
for archived presentations from prior years.  These 
replays may be viewed for free if you are logged in to the 
Embarcadero Developer Network ("EDN").
</whtranslation>

